{
  "stem": "3653.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I'm not a millionaire, but I made a living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Put two kids through college.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I got a house for my daughter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This, I bought a house for.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I helped this daughter too, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But you know, this is the way it goes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But to be along, all right, I have a family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Thanks, God.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But the real family, at least one sister or at least somebody-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I think my father maybe helped me to live through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because all this, every night when it was bad times and camp, beating and killing, I had a dream and I saw my father stays with a tallis.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And even I said to him, what are you doing here, like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I knew right away, I'll have a good day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I will be saved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That's why I go to shul and say kaddish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "If it helps, not helps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But if you believe in this, maybe it's good for you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] I lived through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But I made a mistake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I didn't write a book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thank you for coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
